<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM8.4.3">
<l>viṇṭa malarellā mūtinī yeṉpeṟuti</l>
<l>yaṇṭa mutalva ṉamararka ḷellārum</l>
<l>kaṇṭu vaṇaṅkuṅkaṇ ṇapurat temperumāṉ</l>
<l>vaṇṭu naṟuntuḻāy vantūtāy kōltumpī.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>What do you gain, sipping all the blossomed flowers?</l>
<l>Twiggy dragonfly, come and sip the fragrant tulasī with bees</l>
<l>Of our great lord in Kaṇṇapuram where all immortals worship,</l>
<l>Gazing at the primal lord of the universe.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
